Package: keen-pbr-headless
Version: @VERSION@
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCHITECTURE@
Maintainer: keen-pbr maintainers <noreply@keen-pbr.local>
Depends: @DEPENDS@
Installed-Size: @INSTALLED_SIZE@
Homepage: https://github.com/maksimkurb/keenetic-pbr-go
Description: Policy-based routing daemon without REST API and Web UI
 keen-pbr routes traffic selectively by IPs, CIDRs, and domains.
 This package installs the daemon and helper scripts without the REST API
 or frontend assets.
